We'd end up wanting to include a specific factor, and probably three specific factors (one for gist vs verbatim, anotother for immediate vs delayed). This would not be identified with only four indicators, so we are just going to go with delayed verbatim (RANDTdv) which is probably the most difficult task. This group is relatively high functioning.
